Context should have a timer.
No change should be visible in the context between any two steps of the timer.
The timer should have a current step index.
The timer should have a "next" command that increments the current step index.
The timer should have a "previous" command that decrements the current step index.
The timer should have an initial current step index of zero.
It should not be possible to have a step index which is less than zero.

Context should have a two dimensional space.
Context should have points in space.
